{{Italic title}}
'''''The Journal of Media Law''''' is a biannual [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Hart Publishing]]. It was established in 2009 and is indexed by [[EBSCOhost]], [[Academic Search Complete]], and [[Applied Science & Technology Abstracts]].<ref>"[http://ulrichsweb.serialssolutions.com/title/1327372783885/678670 The Journal of Media Law]." ''[[Ulrich's Periodicals Directory]]''. Retrieved on January 24, 2012.</ref> The [[editors-in-chief]] are Eric Barendt ([[University College London]]), Thomas Gibbons ([[University of Manchester]]), and Rachael Craufurd Smith ([[University of Edinburgh]]).

